{
  "stem": "27285.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was such a joy to have your own book and to open it and to enjoy something completely normal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the freedom of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You went-- we were so fearless when-- we didn't know we are supposed to be afraid of something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You were happy to be alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Not that it was easy afterwards to-- to recognize your parents and-- and find another kind of way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And actually, we had a very, very nice relation after a few time-- after I left my parents to study music in Jerusalem, and until the war came here in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then Israel, I also was wounded here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But that was very easy and happy time nevertheless.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were very, very good nation then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were all together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And also, the way to find my parents was very difficult and compliment--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--complicated in the beginning, but it really was a-- it sounds-- I mean, it sounds like a cliche, but really love really bridged-- [INAUDIBLE] it bridged so beautifully that we found a very, very good relationship in the end, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, so you're finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
